    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icy Tower is  back! A fast-paced platformer where you play as Harold the Homeboy (and his friends) trying to climb as high as possible in an endless tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/0c989b354b6d1eec71972127306be099.avif?t=1770967932\" width=780 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain impossible combo jumps, bounce off walls, and risk everything for insane scores. But one mistake and it is back to the beginning! With its simple pick-up-and-play appeal Icy Tower delivers a pure and compelling gameplay experience like no other. As the difficulty ramps up, Icy Tower will put your timing, precision, and nerves to the ultimate test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/780cfbd3f3659143cadb48fd50e506e3.avif?t=1770967932\" width=780 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brought to you by the creators of the original Icy Tower, this brand new game is remade from the ground  up with a lot of love and passion. Expect silly smooth gameplay and an irresistible feedback loop that will keep you trying again and again..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ Wishlist now and get ready for the 25th anniversary in 2026! 🥳</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/c63650fecfcfa8e883fb3c9977475d6d.avif?t=1770967932\" width=348 height=71 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the tower through diverse themes and biomes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull off combo jumps for sky-high scores!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn kickbacks to save you when you slip!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy live-recorded music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crisp pixel perfect, handcrafted graphics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off with sharable replays!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a diverse cast of characters with unique styles!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/b7d1422b1421fe0eb0c67e1db54b30a9.avif?t=1770967932\" width=271 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icy Tower is made by <strong>Johan Peitz</strong> and <strong>Anders &quot;Neo&quot; Svensson</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character art and animation - <strong>Rudy Flores</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environment art - <strong>Franek</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key art - <strong>Lu Nascimento</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/3c1f67b23edab894fde84ca7a9fa7981.apng?t=1770967932\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/3c1f67b23edab894fde84ca7a9fa7981.poster.avif?t=1770967932\" class=\"bb_img\" width=92 height=88 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/1e09683c16290c4864181c5b633d7332.apng?t=1770967932\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/1e09683c16290c4864181c5b633d7332.poster.avif?t=1770967932\" class=\"bb_img\" width=110 height=100 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/33ca041b610625cf0ecf97b221c709de.apng?t=1770967932\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/33ca041b610625cf0ecf97b221c709de.poster.avif?t=1770967932\" class=\"bb_img\" width=112 height=100 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/13c7cc86814f2baa9bc7a6eecf95b4a4.apng?t=1770967932\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014860/extras/13c7cc86814f2baa9bc7a6eecf95b4a4.poster.avif?t=1770967932\" class=\"bb_img\" width=92 height=88 /></picture></span></p>",
